            "title": "《國企紅籌》華潤醫藥(3320)附屬華潤三九去年純利升18%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社13日專訊》華潤醫藥(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03320:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03320\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03320-HK</a>)公布,附屬公司華潤三九(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:000999:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/000999\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">000999-CN</a>)披露截至去年12月31日止年度盈利約33.68億元(<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>.下同),升18.05%,每股盈利2.63元,升17.41%。扣除非經常性損益之純利約31.2億元,升15%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　該集團指,華潤三九收入276億元,升11.63%,加權平均淨資產收益率17.33%,升1.47個百分點,華潤三九建議每股派息32分,以資本公積金向股東每10股轉增3股。(wh)</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">*有關業績的詳情,請參閱該公司之正式通告</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
